<dl id="n01072n"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01072n">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01072n"> 72(n)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Sweeping reductions </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: A common phrase; see e.g. <i>Popular Science Monthly</i>, December 1921, p.118 <font color="green">[advertisment]</font>: Diamonds at Pre-War Prices <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> Free 1922 Basch De Luxe Diamond Book &mdash; Write See the <mark>sweeping reductions</mark> in this New Basch Book. Rare bargains also in watches, jewelery, silverware, etc. Trials how to judge a diamond. A postcard or letter brings it free &mdash; write now. <br>Raphael transcription: <a name="c05138d" href="c05all.htm#c05138d">VI.C.05:138(d)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
